<item>
            <title>[LU-14313] mount.lustre fails silently when built without server support</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14313</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If mount.lustre was built without server support, attempting to mount a target without the colon that identifies client mounts fails without an error message.&#160; In addition, the exit code is returned to the user is &quot;234&quot; because the code returns -22 instead of 22.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The issue exists in both master and 2.12&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
